# sosbackups project

## Installation

pip install sosbackups

## Running

### Running daemon

`sosbackups -c <conffile> -p <pidfile> --logfile <logfile>`

### Running foreground

`sosbackups -f -c <conffile> -p <pidfile> --logfile <logfile>`
